title: 1 mile north discography (3 albums)
description:
1 mile north is (was?) an ambient/instrumental post-rock duo from new york. they released two studio albums in the early 2000s, then an album of outtakes/demos in 2011.

not-quite ambient, but extremely chill. hypnotic guitar and analogue synthesizers combine to make mesmerizing instrumental music. there's nothing quite like it!



glass wars (2001)
minor shadows (2003)
altare della patria (2011)
